data.title: Muslim Boys Names Final
data.meta_description: Muslim Boys Names Final - Free ebook download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read book online for free. This document provides a foreword and introduction to a guide on baby names for Muslim boys. It encourages generosity towards orphans by quoting a hadith about caring for orphans being rewarded in paradise. It also provides a link to donate to Islamic Relief's Orphan Sponsorship program. The bulk of the document is a table listing popular Arabic baby names for boys along with their meanings.
